verbose_text: Expectedly, both dOASL-3D * and oOASL-3D *, but not dOASL, oOASL, and dOASL-3K *, significantly increased the expression of nine genes (IRF1, IFNalpha, IFNbeta, IFNAR1, JAK1, STAT1, MX1, PKR, and TNFalpha) downstream of MAVS after infecting by CK/0513 virus.
